comments: Nurkic (POR) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Ferguson (OKC) and does not deliver contact.
Westbrook (OKC) does not extend his arm into Lillard (POR) in the post and the contact that occurs is marginal.
Adams (OKC) impedes Nurkic (POR) during the rebound.
Lillard (POR) makes marginal contact with Adams (OKC) and does not affect his ability to defend the jump shot attempt.
Aminu (POR) swipes down and cleanly dislodges the ball from George (OKC) at the end of the drive.
After the ball is cleanly dislodged, Nurkic (POR) is not in a legal guarding position when George (OKC) regains possession of the ball as he jumps A to B into George's body and affects his SQBR.
Correctly called delay of game violation.
Ferguson (OKC) moves laterally into the path of Lillard (POR) on the drive and the contact affects his ability to maintain possession of the ball.
Aminu (POR) briefly places his hand to George's (OKC) body but does not affect his SQBR.
Aminu (POR) cleanly dislodges the ball from George (OKC) after he receives the pass.
George's (OKC) foot is planted and he does not intentionally kick the ball.
Adams (OKC) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Aminu (POR) and does not deliver contact.
Lillard (POR) extends his arm into Westbrook's (OKC) back and dislodges him from his legally obtained position, affecting his ability to get to the rebound.
Nurkic (POR) briefly engages with Adams (OKC), but does not affect his FOM.
George (OKC) removes his hand from the ball and uses his elbow to deliver contact with Nurkic's (POR) head/face during the driving shot attempt.
McCollum (POR) makes marginal contact to Ferguson's (OKC) body that does not affect his shot attempt near the rim.
Nurkic (POR) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Westbrook (OKC) and does not deliver contact.
Nurkic (POR) makes contact with the rim while the ball is in the cylinder.
RLB and RLS show that Adams (OKC) makes contact to Lillard's (POR) arm during his shooting motion which affects his jump shot attempt.
All technical fouls are reviewed by League Operations.
Grant (OKC) makes contact to Nurkic's (POR) body and affects his shot attempt near the rim.
Morris (OKC) extends his arm into Aminu (POR) and dislodges him from his legally obtained position during the rebound.

call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: Westbrook (OKC) loses control of the ball and is the last to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds.
